title: THE SINGING RINGING TREE B & W
description:
This movie is in PAL format, it is region-free and has the original German soundtrack with the BBC English dubbed narration. There are no other spoken languages and no subs.

This was a project I worked on simply to present the movie as it was originally enjoyed in the 1960s by millions of British children who didn\&#039;t have the luxury of colour TV. It is, therefore, presented here in glorious Black and White.

Download the \&#039;1 MIN 30 SEC MOVIE SAMPLE.VOB\&#039; and/or the \&#039;SAMPLE OF MOVIE MENU RESOURCE.mpg\&#039; before downloading the entire 3.93GB movie, just to ensure you\&#039;re not disappointed.

Enjoy !
